org.afplib.afplib

Interface IOC

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SF
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IOCImpl

    public interface IOC
extends SF
    A representation of the model object 'IOC'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Xoa Oset
    • Yoa Oset
    • Xoa Orent
    • Yoa Orent
    • Con Data1
    • XMap
    • YMap
    • Con Data2

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getIOC()
